data.description: This Gorgeous Home in La Paloma is tucked back in a quiet neighborhood on a large corner lot close to the Tascosa Golf Course. It has a grand entrance with spiral staircase & many windows for natural light with gorgeous wood flooring! Large Kitchen with a skylight and Island with the seperate Laundry room off to the side. A great size formal dining area, ready for those home cooked meals and holiday get togethers! Large living room w/fireplace, built-ins & lots of windows. Retreat & relax in the isolated master w/sitting area & large master bathroom with a large Jet tub 2 sinks and a an automatic lighted closet! The 2 bedrooms upstairs share a full bath. Bedroom 4 would make a great space for an office! Home also has surround sound through out.
